title: Cattle Hide Wettings for United States
notes:
Data For 1921 Computed By NBER By Taking 90 Percent Of "Wettings Of All Hides Leather" From The Farmers' Council. Source: Data For 1922-1934 And 1941-1955: Direct From The Farmers' Council Of America. Data For 1935-1954: Commodity Exchange Incorporated, Monthly Supplement To Daily Market Report On Hides, 1939-1941 Issues.

This NBER data series m01223 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.

NBER Indicator: m01223
